	(text "TPS54061 3.3V PSU - 50V Input\n400kHz, 200mA Output\n\nConnect hierarchical labels to root sheet:\n  VIN_PSU -> Input power (up to 50V)\n  +3V3 -> Regulated 3.3V output\n  GND -> Ground"
